# 1Ô∏è‚É£7Ô∏è‚É£ GOVERNANCE CONTROLS

* Only authorized roles can initiate signing
* No signature bypass allowed
* Mandatory dual-signature for contracts
* Signature cannot be deleted
* Revocation logged permanently

